  <brief_title>The Impact of the Implementation of BIS on the Incidence of Postoperative Delirium</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessing the Impact of the Implementation of BIS on the Incidence of Postoperative Delirium - A Monocentre Prospective Trial</official_title>
