  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will investigate the incidence of postoperative POD in patients undergoing non&#xD;
      cardiac surgery under general anesthesia with and without the implementation of the BIS&#xD;
      monitoring.T&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study will compare the incidence of POD after elective non cardiac surgery conducted&#xD;
      under general anesthesia before and after the implementation of BIS monitoring in our&#xD;
      University Hospital.&#xD;
&#xD;
      The POD will be evaluated with the CAM and Nu-DESC tools, which have been adapted for the&#xD;
      greek population.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
